Today’s Fresh Catch is on the Menu
Sit down and enjoy a real seafood extravaganza – all freshly prepared. Our reastaurant’s relaxed, casual atmosphere is the perfect place for you and your family to enjoy a delicious meal and some “Keys” style fun! With over 100 menu items there’s sure to be something for everyone. Choose from Crab, Florida Lobsters, Shrimp or Mahi to name just a few.

It Doesn’t Get AnyFresher Than This
Hang loose and enjoy the live music with a cold beer or a glass of wine while enjoying the view of the Marina. Fishing boats come and go, and today’s catch is unloaded while pelicans stand guard. Experience the freshest seafood and ambience to match at our waterfront restaurant.
